; 主人公の結婚～悪魔再々復活・ブルー再加入まで




;■主人公の結婚

;◇イベント01・結婚式
*wedding_01

; どこかの教会を選んで『結婚する』を選ぶ
;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[iscript]

// 主人公のセックス履歴
game.wife.strip.theo = "裸・幸せ";
for(var i = 0; i < 14; i++)
{
	game.elapse(1);
	var rec = game.wife.getSexRecord(o.テオ, intrandom(2, 3));
	game.wife.addSexRecordAndChangeHeart(rec);
}

[endscript]
;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

; どこかの教会。結婚した主人公夫婦を祝福する。ヒロインは妻の名
@out
@w05
@bg f=0063
@mu f=wedding
[texton]
[マックス f=03]「Congratulations!」[k]
[マリア v=va247 f=01]「Congratulations! Both of you!」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Thanks, guys.」[k]
[ヒロイン] and I were finally able to hold our wedding ceremony with the blessing of everyone in the party and our acquaintances.[k]
[ヒロイン] and I are now officially husband and wife.[k]
[textoff]

; 各ヒロイン別の結婚式シナリオへ（ドワーフだけ別）
@jump storage="heroine01b.scn" target=*theo_wedding cond='game.wife == o.リム'
@jump storage="heroine02b.scn" target=*theo_wedding cond='game.wife == o.クレア'
@jump storage="heroine04b.scn" target=*theo_wedding cond='game.wife == o.ミューズ'
@jump storage="heroine05b.scn" target=*theo_wedding cond='game.wife == o.マルエット'


;◇イベント02・結婚から２週間後・結婚後のパーティー再結成
*wedding_02

; 設定
;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[iscript]
game.protectHeroines = false;
game.playerChara.married = game.wife.married = true;
game.wife.events = [13, 17, 14, 15, 16, 30, 50, 70];	// 新たな宿屋イベントの設定
game.party.recovery();
game.party.supplyClothesToNakedMembers();
o.ブルー.recovery();
o.ライナス.recovery();
o.サンドラ.recovery();

// o.サファイアシティ.events.push(12);
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.events.push2(18);
o.ブレイブタウン・西門.events = [];
o.冒険者の宿.events = [14];
o.ホテル琥珀.events = [3];
o.潮風のペンション.events = [2];
o.雪の宿.events = [1];
o.大洞窟ホテル.events = [0];
o.簡易宿泊所.events = [0, 1];
o.ヤネクの森・霧の谷.events.remove(5);
game.events.push(52);	// 神の山封鎖解除の報告

[endscript]
;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

; 宿屋のロビー。ヒロインは妻の名
@bg f=0003 b
@fg c=マックス f=03
[texton]
[マックス f=03]「Yo! [テオ]! Long time no see! [ヒロイン] too!」[k]

; 結婚した妻のセリフ。夫とともに他のメンバーを迎える
@eval exp='game.curChara = game.wife'
[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh080 e=現在の装備 f=01]「Good morning, [マックス].」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve081 e=現在の装備 f=02]「Good morning, Max.」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd078 e=現在の装備 f=03]「Good morning, [マックス].」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg068 e=現在の装備 f=02]「Good morning, [マックス].」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs082 e=現在の装備 f=01]「Good morning, Max.」[k]
[endif]

; 結婚しなかった他のメンバーのセリフ。テオ夫婦に会いに来た
[if exp='HUM && game.curChara != game.wife']
	[リム v=vh081 f=01]「Captain! It's been a while! I look forward to working with you again!」[k]
[endif]
[if exp='ELF && game.curChara != game.wife']
	[クレア v=ve082 f=02]「Long time no see, Captain. Nice to see you again.」[k]
[endif]
[if exp='DWA && game.curChara != game.wife']
	[フレデリカ v=vd079 f=03]「It's been a long time～ I look forward to working with you again!」[k]
[endif]
[if exp='GNO && game.curChara != game.wife']
	[ミューズ v=vg069 f=02]「It's been a while... Please take care of me again, Captain.」[k]
[endif]
[if exp='SYL && game.curChara != game.wife']
	[マルエット v=vs083 f=01]「It's been a while! I look forward to working with you again!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ e=現在の装備 f=02]「Yeah, good to see you again, everyone.」[k]
[ライナス f=06]「...Yo.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Linus, you're here too. I hope we can continue to work together.」[k]
For now, it seems we are all here. After a long break, everyone in the party will adventure together again.[k]
I greeted the new morning with a very refreshed feeling.[k]
Now, there are no more demons and no more involvement with Blue. Alight, it's all up to us what we want to do from here on out.[k]
We can take on new quests at the tavern, or venture out into uncharted territory.[k]
Now, what should I do first...?[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@eval exp='game.churchWin.visible = false'
[eventoff]


;◇イベント03・冒険再開初日の宿予約時のコメント
*wedding_03

; 宿のロビー。ヒロインは妻の名
@w05
[texton]
[テオ]「Well, I guess we'll rest here tonight.」[k]
Our party arrives at the inn. We are now going to assign rooms.[k]
But now, [ヒロイン] and I are a married couple.[k]
In other words, unless there are special circumstances, I have to share a room with [ヒロイン].[k]
I mustn't make the mistake of staying with another woman, because that would seriously undermine [ヒロイン]'s trust in me.[k]
[textoff]
[hoteloff]




;■悪魔再々復活とブルー再加入

;◇イベント01・ダストウェルの町に到着
*revive_1

; ダストウェルの町
@w05
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「This is the forgotten town...!」[k]
How much time had passed since we started walking through the desert?[k]
There was indeed a "forgotten town". Its name was Dustwell.[k]
Deep in a valley in the middle of the wilderness, a town of some size had been built. Who would have thought that a town could exist in such a remote place...[k]
[テオ f=06]「Well... First we have to find a place to stay...」[k]
Everyone is tired from all the walking. First of all, let's stay somewhere and heal from the fatigue of the trip.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント02・シュバルツの話
*revive_2

; ダストウェルの町
@saveon
@w05
[texton w=0]
Next morning.[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=シュバルツ f=00
[texton w=1]
[シュバルツ]「Oh, there you are! I've been looking for you, [テオ].」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Mr. Schwartz, it's been a long time. I see that you know of this town too.」[k]
To my surprise, I ran into that Mr. Schwartz in this isolated town. As expected of him, he knew even this remote area.[k]
Although... I could tell from Mr. Schwartz's grim expression that he wasn't in the mood to celebrate our reunion.[k]
[テオ f=05]「You said you were looking for me.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「[テオ], you're in danger.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Is there something wrong?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「The devil...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
@fa
[シュバルツ f=07]「The devil... Murmur has risen again!」[k]
[if exp='game.wife !== void'][ヒロイン f=11]「...!」[k][endif]
[テオ f=12]「What did you say?!」[k]
@mu f=cave
Murmur is back...?! That's impossible...![k]
She died in the last battle. She was burned to ashes by the flames of Sandra's magic.[k]
I saw Murmur reduced to ashes with my own eyes. This time it was certain destruction.[k]
She... she can't be alive![k]
[テオ f=12]「I-is that really true?!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=10]「Believe it or not, it's true. I've seen it with my own eyes.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Oh no...」[k]
I can't believe it. I want to believe it's a lie.[k]
We went through a lot of hardship to confront that devil. I hope it's a mistake.[k]
...But Mr. Schwartz is not the kind of person to make such a careless mistake.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Mr. Schwartz, could you tell us more about this?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「Yes, of course. Please, listen.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「Have you seen that big canyon west of Collins Wood?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「One day, I heard a rumor that someone was building a mysterious tower there, and decided to investigate. And there she was...!」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

; 塔の建設現場。シュバルツの回想
@bg f=0041
@fg c=悪魔 f=07
[texton w=1]
[ムールムール v=vm211 f=07]「Hey, you! You guys better get to work!」[k]
[name n=Worker f=thief_blue_02]「Ugh...」[k]
[name n=Worker f=thief_red_02]「Please... Let me rest now...」[k]
@se f=whip
@flash time=200
∗crack!∗[k]
[name n=Worker f=thief_blue_02]「Waaaaah!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm212 f=07]「I told you not to take a break! I'll kill you!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=10]「...」[k]
On the top floor of a tower under construction, I saw many men working on the construction and Murmur whipping them.[k]
I watched from a small hill a short distance away so that she would not see me. But there was no doubt in my mind that the figure and voice was Murmur's.[k]
[ムールムール v=vm213 f=07]「You know what? I can kill you all with my breath of death anytime I want! So don't dare disobey me!」[k]
[name n=Worker f=thief_blue_02]「Ugh...」[k]
[name n=Worker f=thief_red_02]「D-damn!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm214 f=07]「I want to make this tower even taller! It's not high enough at all!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm215 f=07]「I have to finish the tower before the gods get wind of this! I'm in a hurry, get it?! So work harder!」[k]
@se f=whip
@flash time=200
∗crack!∗[k]
[name n=Worker f=thief_blue_02]「Waaaaah!」[k]
[name n=Worker f=thief_red_02]「All right, all right, I'll work. So don't kill me...!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=10]「Damn... That Murmur...!」[k]
By my estimate, the tower was about 10 stories high. She said she would make it higher.[k]
I wanted to help them, but if she found me, I would have been the target of her fatal breath. All I could do was watch.[k]
[ムールムール v=vm216 f=03]「Gahahahaha! Hey, hey, hey! Work harder～!」[k]
; ↑ 爆笑しながら
@se f=whip
@flash time=200
@wait time=500
@se f=whip
@flash time=200
∗crack!∗ ∗crack!∗[k]
[name n=Worker f=thief_blue_02]「Gyaaaaaah!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=10]「...」[k]
After observing the situation for a while, I quietly left so that she wouldn't see me...[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05
@gameon
@fgf c=シュバルツ f=00
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=05]「Murmur is building a tower...?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「Yes. She wants her large human workforce to build her a very tall tower.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What on earth for...?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「I don't know her motives. But since it's her, she's surely up to no good.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I'm worried about the people who are forced to work there. It needs to be stopped...」[k]
She said, "I want to destroy the human world and make it a world ruled by demons". As long as her goal remains unchanged, there is nothing to do but oppose her plans.[k]
But... I guess that devil really is back...[k]
...Damn! I guess a high-ranking demon cannot be completely destroyed by human power...![k]
No matter how much you cut them up, no matter how much you reduce them to ashes, they will resurrect. That's the power of such devils.[k]
They are beings we cannot be fathom. As living organisms, they are far superior to humans.[k]
Then, the only way is to seal her away. To do so, we need the help of the god Polaris.[k]
In other words... the only way to fundamentally resolve this issue is to summon the god Polaris with the 12 magic stones...[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「What is it? Are you still in shock?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Yes... Just when I thought things were finally at peace...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「...It will be hard, but only you, the demon hunter, can do it. Please do your best. I will help you as much as I can.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Thank you, Mr. Schwarz.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「Well, that's all for now.」[k]
@cl
Yes, this is no time to be depressed. It's hard, but we have to fight.[k]
To protect this world... And to protect my party friends and my beloved [ヒロイン], I have no choice but to defeat the devil.[k][endif]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[if exp='game.getNumOfJewels(true) >= 12']
	I have collected 12 magic stones. If I go to the Temple of Polaris right now, I should be able to summon Lady Polaris.[k]
	However, the Temple of Polaris is very far from here. If it's attacked before we reach it...[k]
[else]
	Currently, we have [emb exp='game.getNumOfJewels(true)'] magic stones that we have collected. We haven't been able to collect all 12 yet.[k]
	Right now, Murmur seems to be obsessed with building a tower, but you never know when she might decide to come and kill us.[k]
	If she attacks us while we're collecting the rest of the magic stones...[k]
[endif]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I need to think of a solution. What should we do...?[k]
[textoff]
