[texton]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
In the end... I guess we have to rely on him once again.[k]
[textoff]
@jump target=*_kick_out_from_dustwell cond='game.wife === void'
@fg c=ライナス f=06
[texton w=1]
[ライナス f=06]「I'm out of here. I don't want to fight that demon anymore.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I can't say I blame you. Thanks for everything, Linus.」[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.ライナス)'
@se f=period
