[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd083 f=14]「It's okay, dear. I can handle Blue. Don't worry.」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg073 f=08]「It's okay... I can handle Blue... So don't worry...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs087 f=36]「It's okay, my love, I can handle Blue. So don't worry.」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=10]「Even if you say it's okay...」[k]
Letting another man hold [ヒロイン]... I can't do that...[k]
...It's true that I'm only thinking about my own convenience right now. Blue is right.[k]
The reason I'm refusing Blue's proposal is simply because I don't want my precious [ヒロイン] to be embraced by someone else... that's how I feel.[k]
Am I unfit to be a leader?[k]
[ブルー f=02]「So, what are you going to do? Accept the conditions? Or not?」[k]

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh086 f=08]「I'll do it. That's okay, right?」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve087 f=19]「I'll do it! That's fine, isn't it?」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd084 f=07]「I'll do it. That's okay, right?」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg074 f=06]「I'll do it. It's fine...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs088 f=07]「I'll do it! It's fine!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=12]「[ヒロイン]!」[k]

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh087 f=02]「I understand. I know you care about me. I'm your wife, but I'm a member of this party too.」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve088 f=01]「I understand. I know you care about me. But while I'm your wife, I am also a member of this party.」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd085 f=13]「I understand. I know you care about me. But as well as your wife, I'm also a member of this party.」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg075 f=06]「I understand... that you care about me. But while I'm your wife, I'm also a member of this party...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs089 f=02]「I understand. I know you care about me. Yes I'm your wife, but I'm also a member of this party.」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=10]「...」[k]

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh088 f=04]「Don't worry. My feelings for you won't change... I love you.」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve089 f=22]「Don't worry. My feelings for you will never change. I love you.」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd086 f=04]「Please don't worry. My feelings for you will never change... I love you.」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg076 f=16]「Don't worry... My feelings for you will never change... I love you...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs090 f=23]「Don't worry. My feelings for you will never change. I love you.」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=10]「[ヒロイン]...」[k]
...If [ヒロイン] says so... Then I should believe her.[k]
I shouldn't be hesitant. As a leader, I have a responsibility to protect everyone. Perhaps I should rely on her determination in this situation.[k]
[ブルー f=02]「...It's settled then. Okay, I'll go along with you guys one more time. Don't forget your promise, [テオ].」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[サンドラ f=56]「...」[k]
I could only remain silent.[k]
[ヒロイン] is mine alone, and I won't let anyone take her away from me. I hold back the urge to shout this out loud.[k]
Do I really have no choice but to accept this situation?![k]
[textoff]
@eval exp='game.guest.entry(o.ブルー)'
@eval exp='game.guest.entry(o.サンドラ)'
@st
@se f=up3
@notice text="<y>Sandra and Blue have joined the party!"
@out
@w05
@mu f=&'game.townView.curTown.bgm'
@addevent name=ベトリヌスの酒場 num=13 cond='! o.売春組織の実体を暴け.accepted'
[eventoff bgm]


;◇イベント04・ブルーに初めて妻を差し出す
*revive_4
; ブルーとヒロインの宿泊初日
@return cond='f.replayMode'
@saveon
@bg f=0002
@mu f=worry
[texton w=1]
[テオ e=通常 f=10]「...」[k]
Night has finally come. Starting tonight, I have to offer [ヒロイン] to Blue.[k]
[textoff]
@fg l=ヒロイン e=通常 f=10 b
@fg r=ブルー e=通常 f=02
[texton w=1]
[ブルー f=02]「Yo.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「I'm sure you understand, but starting tonight, your wife is mine.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「See you later. I'm borrowing your wife.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Hey, Blue, do I really have to leave [ヒロイン] with you?」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Of course. That's the deal, right? If you can't keep your promise, I'm leaving the party right now.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Is there no other condition...?」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Rejected. I won't accept anything but what we agreed. Give up already.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
Blue's attitude left no room for discussion. I tried to negotiate with Blue, clinging to a glimmer of hope, but he wouldn't even give me a chance to negotiate.[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Well, I'll do my best to take care of you. See you later.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「W-wait...!」[k]
@se f=door1
@clf
Blue took [ヒロイン] and entered the room.[k]
I am filled with anxiety. To let another man embrace my precious wife...![k]
What's more, the opponent is Blue. Blue is the man who once enslaved Riselle sexually.[k]
What if my beloved [ヒロイン] started to desire sex with that man more than anything else?[k]
[テオ f=09]「...Damn!」[k]
I'm getting impatient. My head is filled with the fear of losing [ヒロイン].[k]
Damn it...! What should I do...?[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w05
@return




;■ポラリスとの会話

; ポラリスの神殿を訪れたとき、祭壇で見えないポラリス神と会話が行われる

;◇パターン１・ゴーレム騒動のさなか、最初にムールムールを倒した後
*polaris_1

; ポラリスの神殿・祭壇
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Lady Polaris, are you there?」[k]
I went to the altar of the Temple of Polaris and called Lady Polaris, in the heavens.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp034 f=polaris_99]「Yes, I'm here.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Actually, we defeated the demon Murmur!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp035 f=polaris_99]「Is that true?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yes, I happened to be nearby when she appeared near Sapphire City, and I took care of it myself! Now that devil is no longer a threat.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp036 f=polaris_99]「Is that so...」[k]
; ↑ あまり喜んでいない。本当に倒せたか疑っている
[テオ f=05]「？」[k]
Despite the long-awaited report that the demon had been defeated, Lady Polaris' reaction was less than favorable.[k]
[ポラリス f=polaris_99]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Lady Polaris, what's wrong?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp037 f=polaris_99]「...Well, I just wonder if it could really be so easy...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What do you mean?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp038 f=polaris_99]「Murmur is, after all, a high-ranking demon. She is not an opponent who can be easily defeated. I don't mean to doubt you all, but...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp039 f=polaris_99]「Please be careful just in case. It may not truly be over. Also, just in case, I would like you to continue collecting magic stones if possible.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...Understood.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp040 f=polaris_99]「I hope it's just my imagination...」[k]
Lady Polaris seems a little hesitant. It might indeed be better to be careful.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇パターン２・ミレディがムールムールであることが発覚した後
*polaris_2

; ポラリスの神殿・祭壇
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Lady Polaris, are you there?」[k]
I went to the altar of the Temple of Polaris and called Lady Polaris, in the heavens.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp034 f=polaris_99]「Yes, I'm here.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...It's Murmur. Just as you suspected, she has been revived.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp041 f=polaris_99]「I knew it...!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Also, the power I had to exorcise demons has been taken away from me. Is there any way I can regain this power?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp042 f=polaris_99]「I'm afraid I can do nothing about that... Being in the heavenly realm, I cannot exert my power over you all...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Is that so...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp043 f=polaris_99]「I'm sorry I couldn't be of help...」[k]
Even Lady Polaris can't do anything about it... For now I have no choice but to accept the current circumstances.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇パターン３・ムールムールと再戦しサンドラの魔法でムールムールを灰にした後
*polaris_3

; ポラリスの神殿・祭壇
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Lady Polaris, are you there?」[k]
I went to the altar of the Temple of Polaris and called Lady Polaris, in the heavens.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp044 f=polaris_99]「Yes, I'm here. What's the matter?」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Lady Polaris! Actually...」[k]
I told her that we had defeated Murmur again and turned her to ash with magic.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp045 f=polaris_99]「I see! That's a relief for now.」[k]
; ↑ 今度は本気で喜んでいる
[ポラリス v=vp046 f=polaris_99]「Thank you very much for your long-standing efforts. We deeply appreciate your courage in confronting the devil.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What should I do with the magic stones I've collected?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp047 f=polaris_99]「Please keep hold of them for now.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp048 f=polaris_99]「Murmur has been destroyed, but there are still many other demons out there. Could you keep them in storage in case something else happens?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Understood.」[k]
That's right. Just like with Malphas last time, there is a possibility that another demon will appear. It is necessary to be prepared for the next time something happens.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇パターン４・灰になったムールムールが復活したことをシュバルツから知らされた後
*polaris_4

; ポラリスの神殿・祭壇
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Lady Polaris, are you there?」[k]
I went to the altar of the Temple of Polaris and called Lady Polaris, in the heavens.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp044 f=polaris_99]「Yes, I'm here. What's the matter?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Lady Polaris! Actually...」[k]
I reported that Murmur, who had previously been reduced to ashes, had been revived.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp049 f=polaris_99]「I see... It's not so easy to get rid of her after all...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「We reduced her to ashes once. This time, we thought we had defeated her. But then...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp050 f=polaris_99]「That's what demons are like... No matter how much you burn them or cut them up, they will always come back to life. Unless they are sealed away with divine power.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp051 f=polaris_99]「...It seems that I have no choice but to leave. Adventurer, will you please gather all 12 magic stones? Once the magic stones are gathered, I will be able to descend to the earth.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I guess that's the only way...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp052 f=polaris_99]「It will be difficult, but please do your best. The fate of the earth depends on your efforts.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Yes... To be honest, there are many obstacles, but I will try harder...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp053 f=polaris_99]「Sorry, thank you very much...」[k]
In the end, there's no choice but to take the direct approach... The repeated futile efforts are enough to break my spirit.[k]
However, I cannot give up now. This time, I will defeat that devil and restore true peace.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇パターン５・魔石が１２個で、オニキスの魔石（ニセモノ）が混じっている時の会話
*polaris_5
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*polaris_5 cond='game.isFreeMode'
; ポラリスの神殿・祭壇
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Huh...? There's one crystal that isn't glowing.」[k]
That's strange... we definitely collected 12 magic stones, but one of them isn't glowing. What on earth is going on?![k]
[ポラリス v=vp054 f=polaris_99]「...There's a fake mixed in there.」[k]
Lady Polaris answered.[k]
[テオ f=12]「A fake?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp055 f=polaris_99]「Among the 12 magic stones you collected, there is one fake. Someone must have made a clever imitation of the real thing. Magic stones sell for a high price.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Oh, no...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp056 f=polaris_99]「There must be a genuine magic stone somewhere. Please search for it. I know it's going to be difficult, but...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I understand. I'll try looking for it again.」[k]
How humiliating. I can't believe I was tricked into buying a fake. I'd been desperately trying to collect magic stones up until now...[k]
...There's no point in being discouraged. We'll have to pull ourselves together and search for the last one again. We're almost there.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


